text: Gulyukovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Starobaishevsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 181 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Dyurtyuli, 5 km from Starobaishevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Gulyukovo
